⫻kicklang:header
# Escalation Protocol

⫻context/escalate:trigger
User request: "Escalate"

⫻data/escalate:reason
Task requires external info/decision beyond scope.

⫻gen/escalate:action
1. Pause current task.
2. Notify user: "Escalation required. Reason: [reason]".
3. Log event.
4. Await input.

⫻context/escalate:example
User: "Escalate"
System: "Escalation required. Reason: External decision needed."
User: [provides input]
System: Resume/Adjust task.
